extendedInfo.description: Cat Diet Calculator will help you calculate your cat's dietary needs. Information is provided on over 50 breeds of cats and almost 900 types of cat food. Answer questions in a simple step-by-step process and you will be provided with breed information, dietary requirements, and weight loss requirements for your cat.

reviews.comment: Gives you info about each breed of cat and the calories in many cat foods. However, can not search for specific foods and the layout needs improved.
reviews.author: A Google User
